            "name": "about",
            "settings": {
                "eyebrow": "About us",
                "body": "<p>At WODI's daycare, we believe childhood should be joyful, meaningful, and full of wonder. Our caring and experienced teachers nurture creativity, confidence, and curiosity every single day. Through play based learning and guided exploration we help.</p>",
